### patch title to a duplicate ("Her", movie 6) — expect 400 (title rule applies on PATCH too)
PATCH {{MovieApi_HostAddress}}/api/movies/1
Content-Type: application/json-patch+json

[
  {
    "op": "replace",
    "path": "/title",
    "value": "Her"
  }
]

