### Shawshank (movie 2, 1994) seeded with 8 staggered reviews — each shows a distinct createdAt
### Before Step 30 exists: 8 reviews (oldest = Cara ~8 days ago, newest = Karin ~1 day ago).
### After Step 30 (trimmer running): 5 reviews — the newest (Greta, Hans, Ingrid, Jonas, Karin); Cara/Dan/Eve trimmed.
GET {{MovieApi_HostAddress}}/api/movies/2/reviews
Accept: application/json

###

### Her (movie 6, 2013) is recent, so the trimmer leaves it alone even with 9 reviews
GET {{MovieApi_HostAddress}}/api/movies/6/reviews
Accept: application/json

